39:11.600 --> 39:15.652
Hey, hey.
You don't have to do this.

39:15.771 --> 39:21.024
But I really want to.

39:23.412 --> 39:25.579
[whimpering]

39:25.664 --> 39:27.330
Hey!

39:55.477 --> 39:57.811
You can't hurt me.
He won't allow it.

39:57.896 --> 40:04.067
Oh, yeah?
Then he won't mind if I do this.

40:09.324 --> 40:11.324
<i>[blow lands]
[Declan laughs]</i>

40:11.410 --> 40:13.376
[laughing]

40:14.463 --> 40:16.079
What's so funny?

40:16.164 --> 40:20.583
You have no idea how
insignificant you really are.

40:21.753 --> 40:24.054
That makes two of us, pal.

40:24.172 --> 40:25.972
Declan!

40:26.058 --> 40:28.475
[screams]

40:32.931 --> 40:34.180
Hood!

40:34.266 --> 40:35.815
[panting]

40:41.023 --> 40:43.156
[gunshot]

40:51.917 --> 40:54.584
<i>[police radio chatter]</i>

41:01.599 --> 41:04.362
[music]

41:19.895 --> 41:22.195
Is that the man that killed my niece?

41:24.900 --> 41:26.366
Yeah.

41:26.367 --> 41:29.192
[music]

41:44.252 --> 41:46.169
Thank you.

41:53.512 --> 41:55.345
<i>Thank you.</i>

42:17.035 --> 42:18.918
[beeping]

42:19.004 --> 42:21.171
<i>[lock whirs, clicks]</i>

42:23.208 --> 42:26.509
<i>[distant siren wailing]</i>

42:34.636 --> 42:36.553
<i>[computer beeps]</i>

42:39.224 --> 42:41.827
<i>[beeps]
[music]</i>

42:48.483 --> 42:50.283
[beeping]

42:53.789 --> 42:55.705
<i>Job: Don't bother.</i>

42:59.803 --> 43:02.154
[gasps]

43:02.747 --> 43:04.330
Job.

43:05.467 --> 43:10.503
- You remembered.
- I have money, Job.

43:10.589 --> 43:12.472
Lots of it.

43:12.557 --> 43:16.509
- You have no idea.
- 23.62 million.

43:16.645 --> 43:19.345
Not counting the 5.2
million in Swiss francs

43:19.481 --> 43:21.681
<i>you have stashed away in the Caymans.</i>

43:21.817 --> 43:24.934
Or rather I should say
"you had."

43:26.071 --> 43:29.989
What did you do with my money?
[chuckles]

43:30.075 --> 43:33.109
Oh, honey, that ain't
your money no more.

43:33.195 --> 43:35.528
What do you want?

43:35.614 --> 43:38.198
[sighs]

43:38.333 --> 43:40.533
What do I want?

43:48.043 --> 43:50.043
I want...

43:50.128 --> 43:54.430
20 months of my
motherfucking life back.

43:54.549 --> 43:56.633
It wasn't personal.

43:56.718 --> 44:01.271
But you're right.
I fucked you.

44:01.389 --> 44:04.607
<i>We can put the past behind us.</i>

44:04.726 --> 44:09.195
- Imagine what you and I could do...
- 20 months!

44:12.901 --> 44:18.571
20 months
of planning all the things

44:18.707 --> 44:22.041
I was going to do
when I got out.

44:24.045 --> 44:27.580
All the things I was going to do...

44:30.385 --> 44:33.753
to the motherfucker who put me there.

44:37.008 --> 44:38.091
[whimpers]

44:39.344 --> 44:42.095
[breathing heavily]

44:42.180 --> 44:46.532
But I have since seen the light.

44:47.485 --> 44:50.153
[panting]

44:50.272 --> 44:51.821
Erasing your worthless ass

44:51.940 --> 44:55.536
ain't gonna give me
back the time you took.

44:56.778 --> 45:01.414
- You're not going to kill me?
- No.

45:01.499 --> 45:05.418
<i>I'm going to kill me.
[beeps]</i>

45:06.788 --> 45:09.839
You wanted to fuck with the best.

45:09.958 --> 45:12.508
Well, now you are the best.

45:13.545 --> 45:15.845
Now you are Job.

45:15.964 --> 45:19.299
From now on, anytime
anybody comes looking for me,

45:19.434 --> 45:23.937
they're gonna find you.
Every security system I ever cracked,

45:24.022 --> 45:26.439
<i>every organization I ever compromised,</i>

45:26.524 --> 45:28.141
<i>every dollar I ever stole,</i>

45:28.276 --> 45:31.144
<i>they all got your
fingerprints on them now.</i>

45:31.279 --> 45:34.113
<i>Mossad, People's Republic,</i>

45:34.199 --> 45:37.900
<i>Uncle Sam, and a who's who
of unsavory terrorist types,</i>

45:37.986 --> 45:40.403
<i>they all got serious beef
with you now.</i>

45:40.488 --> 45:44.991
Bitch, I just made your punk ass famous.

45:46.161 --> 45:47.961
And something tells me...

45:51.333 --> 45:54.917
you gonna be a hell of a lot
easier to find than I ever was.

46:03.228 --> 46:07.430
- Have a nice short life, motherfucker.
- Job, wait.

46:07.515 --> 46:10.800
You can't do this to me!

46:13.989 --> 46:15.772
Job!

46:39.931 --> 46:42.215
[crying]

46:48.157 --> 46:51.858
