47:22.624 --> 47:25.692
<i>♪ This town ain't changed ♪
[music]</i>

47:25.794 --> 47:28.628
<i>♪ It's still the same ♪</i>

47:28.730 --> 47:31.731
<i>♪ This town ain't changed ♪</i>

47:31.833 --> 47:34.367
<i>♪ And it knows my name ♪</i>

47:49.084 --> 47:50.750
<i>♪ I still remember ♪</i>

47:50.852 --> 47:54.887
<i>♪ All the ways you took me down ♪</i>

47:54.989 --> 48:00.526
<i>♪ You're every corner of
this godforsaken town ♪</i>

48:01.663 --> 48:04.797
<i>♪ Like a river breaking stone ♪</i>

48:04.899 --> 48:07.600
<i>♪ Beneath the ground ♪</i>

48:07.702 --> 48:10.269
<i>♪ We are the future ♪</i>

48:10.371 --> 48:12.805
<i>♪ We are bound. ♪</i>

